Class ActionPlanViolation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.castsoftware.jira.pojo.ActionPlanViolation

  • public class ActionPlanViolation
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class ActionPlanViolation is used to store every violation included in the action plan. It will provide and easy way to interact with every violation

    1.1
